block headAdditions
  title How to use

block content
  h2 Edition Guidelines

  small (preliminary version)

  ul
    li All the original clefs are preserved, since it's possible to replace them automatically with modern clefs but not vice versa
    li Accidentals are adapted to modern use
    li Original double bar lines at the end of a piece are adapted to the modern practice
    li Obvious and clear mistakes are corrected
    li Editorial addition are marked as #[code <supplied>]
    li The text is generally preserved in its original orthography, including the different letter-spacing.
       | However, for the sake of easier readability all #[code /] are replaced by #[code ,]
    li Linebreaks are not (yet) preserved
    li Musical meters in the text are encoded using a #[code /]
